        class='font-fraunces text-[32px] md:text-2xl lg:text-[40px] md:leading-tight font-black tracking-[-0.229px] mb-6 md:mb-5 lg:mb-8 text-center md:text-left text-stone-950'
      >
        Stand out to the right audience
      </h2>
      <p
        class='text-stone-600 text-center md:text-left text-lg md:text-sm lg:text-lg font-semibold leading-[30px] tracking-custom mb-8 md:mb-7 lg:mb-10'
      >
        Using a collaborative formula of designers, researchers, photographers, videographers, and
