      <div class='flex flex-col gap-7 items-center justify-between md:min-h-36 md:justify-start'>
        <h2
          class='font-fraunces text-[28px] font-black tracking-[-0.2px] text-green-800 md:bg-white md:bg-opacity-80 md:px-4 lg:bg-transparent'
        >
          Graphic Design
        </h2>
        <p
          class='text-green-800 font-semibold leading-[27px] tracking-[-0.114px] text-center lg:max-w-[340px]'
        >
          Great design makes you memorable. We deliver artwork that underscores your brand message
          and captures potential clients' attention.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class={`flex flex-col justify-end justify relative pb-[60px] aspect-[5/8] md:aspect-[6/5] px-6 bg-[url('/mobile/image-photography.jpg')] md:bg-[url('/desktop/image-photography.jpg')] bg-contain bg-center`}
