      <p class='text-center text-stone-700 text-lg font-semibold leading-[32px] tracking-custom'>
        Incredible end result! Our sales increased over 400% when we worked with Sunnyside. Highly
        recommended!
      </p>
      <div class='flex flex-col gap-[9px] text-center'>
        <p class='font-fraunces text-stone-950 text-lg font-black tracking-custom'>Jennie F.</p>
        <p class='text-stone-400 text-sm font-semibold leading-[25px] tracking-[-0.1px]'>
